Addition
========

Basic addition with 32-bit integers.

| Scenario     | X            | Y            | X + Y      |
|--------------|-------------:|-------------:|-----------:|
| simple add   | 1            | 2            | 3          |
| zero left    | 0            | 2            | 2          |
| zero right   | 1            | 0            | 1          |
| zero both    | 0            | 0            | 0          |
